# Dollar-weighted return: sum(cf*time) / sum(cf).
*dwr(cf as Vec of i64, t as Vec of i64, n as i64) returns i64
    num is 0
    den is 0
    i is 0
    while i < n
        num is num + cf.get(i) * t.get(i)
        den is den + cf.get(i)
        i is i + 1
    if den equals 0
        return 0
    num / den

*main
    c is vec()
    c.push(100)
    c.push(200)
    c.push(50)
    t is vec()
    t.push(1)
    t.push(5)
    t.push(10)
    log dwr(c, t, 3)
